PortSystem 1.0
name			ddrescue
version			1.0
categories		sysutils
maintainers		opendarwin@cybozone.com
description		GNU ddrescue is a data recovery tool. It copies data from one \
				file or	block device (hard disc, cdrom, etc) to another, \
				trying hard to rescue data in case of read errors.
homepage		http://www.gnu.org/software/ddrescue/ddrescue.html
master_sites		gnu:ddrescue
checksums		md5 0acd5df3f860eba20c01f317b40b8516
use_bzip2		yes
